OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will be cloudy with some rain
OL,8,Fspreading to west counties, remaining
OL,9,Fdry across the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,12,Fspreading eastwards across all parts
OL,13,Fin the morning. Drier weather
OL,14,Ffollowing on behind during the
OL,15,Fafternoon, reaching the east coast by
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
